    - Litigation
  document_types:
    - Summary
  skill_modes:
    - Summarization
    - Analysis
---
```

## Output

Return ONLY the complete SKILL.md content. No explanations, no markdown code fences wrapping it, no commentary. Just the raw file content starting with `---` and ending with the last line of the skill.


